Crispy Frozen Waffles with Fresh Toppings

10 min
$3.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

VegetarianLow Sodium

Description

Deliciously crispy waffles topped with fresh fruits and a drizzle of honey.

Ingredients

  • frozen waffles: 2 pieces
  • fresh strawberries: 1/2 cup
  • banana: 1 medium
  • honey: 1 tablespoon
